    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Become part of an elite special forces unit in Tactical Assault VR!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tactical Assault VR is an intense tactical shooter where you use real-world CQB (Close Quarters Battles) tactics to stack up, breach doors and eliminate threats. Play solo or join an online co-op special forces unit in missions around the world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PvE Missions: Solo or Online Multiplayer Co-Op with Up to 8 Players on PCVR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/89188aef56ba00d83e1b7ebd67370e68.poster.avif?t=1766233209\" width=614 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/89188aef56ba00d83e1b7ebd67370e68.webm?t=1766233209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/89188aef56ba00d83e1b7ebd67370e68.mp4?t=1766233209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PvP: Competitive Online Multiplayer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/b6a9d070a021f28e736686a14e34b479.poster.avif?t=1766233209\" width=614 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/b6a9d070a021f28e736686a14e34b479.webm?t=1766233209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/b6a9d070a021f28e736686a14e34b479.mp4?t=1766233209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >7 Non-Linear, Asymmetrical Maps</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plan your assault. The choice is yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/87a4fe2bf125cdf7aae529b7d91be72f.poster.avif?t=1766233209\" width=614 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/87a4fe2bf125cdf7aae529b7d91be72f.webm?t=1766233209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/87a4fe2bf125cdf7aae529b7d91be72f.mp4?t=1766233209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hostile Surrendering and Arresting</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/0641f5d2fc961fa122e808e0f9331f02.poster.avif?t=1766233209\" width=614 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/0641f5d2fc961fa122e808e0f9331f02.webm?t=1766233209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/0641f5d2fc961fa122e808e0f9331f02.mp4?t=1766233209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Mode Variety</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bomb Defusal, Hostage Rescue, High Value Target (HVT) Eliminations, Mini Games, Room Randomizer Killhouse, Shootout (wave shooter)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/afc6f7b4f2837a0b76070fb07f553b6c.poster.avif?t=1766233209\" width=614 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/afc6f7b4f2837a0b76070fb07f553b6c.webm?t=1766233209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/afc6f7b4f2837a0b76070fb07f553b6c.mp4?t=1766233209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >30+ Detailed Weapons and Counting</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your loadout with tactical gear including vests, helmets, weapons, scopes, sights, grips, and breaching equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/17b69e9c614d831d178835bba96d887c.poster.avif?t=1766233209\" width=614 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/17b69e9c614d831d178835bba96d887c.webm?t=1766233209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/17b69e9c614d831d178835bba96d887c.mp4?t=1766233209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join the Discord and Find Your Squad</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/d6848e5b3792a931c21a10d439c41f83.poster.avif?t=1766233209\" width=614 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/d6848e5b3792a931c21a10d439c41f83.webm?t=1766233209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314160/extras/d6848e5b3792a931c21a10d439c41f83.mp4?t=1766233209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
